{"tid":1706903,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"從來都唔應該問[裝修] 、[鶳]、[割頸]、[拆鐵] 等等割唔割","createTime":"2019-11-11T07:48:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-11T11:35:06.000Z","uid":81236,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"9cb978c3cac061e598e76200bfeef9cb4d0be1bc","tid":1706903,"uid":81236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T07:48:24.000Z","msg":"應該係問做得夠唔夠好<br />\n<br />\n問割唔割有咩意思？你都係問人不如割姐。<br />\n<br />\n就算今日火燒藍絲廢老<br />\n<br />\n都只係覺得今次做得唔夠好，要改善<br />\n<br />\n問人割唔割之前，你有冇見過幾多藍絲廢老拎刀攻擊手足？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\">又唔見藍絲問割唔割，佢地甚至會讚好<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n所以唔好再問割唔割，就算果隻係鬼係臥底扮手足做以上既事<br />\n<br />\n方向都應該係問夠唔夠好，唔夠好就改善，因為佢地都係同一方向<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後附上立場有關屠龍小隊專訪，因字數有限，最低有link<br />\n<br />\n但有三點好值得大家參考<br />\n<br />\n1）<span style=\"color: red;\">「你一做就做到底，一係就唔好做，半桶水反而令人覺得，唔知你做緊咩。」</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2）<span style=\"color: red;\">無法理解，為何會有人用「火魔法」來燒路障雜物，甚至無故掟向地面，浪費「難能可貴」的珍貴資源，「唔應該同嚟燒死物，或者掉落地。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n3）作用，George 一直反覆強調這兩個字，就是行動要有成效，能針對警方、或增加政府管治成本，所以難以置信又合乎情理地，一直在前線和警方肉搏的「屠龍小隊」，至今都沒有參與過任何「私了」，「我希望手足，可以將情緒發洩係政權、警隊，而唔係所謂藍絲、廢老。」是否因為「私了」會被割蓆失分？「唔係，我個目標一定要政權回應訴求，任何行動去令政權管治成本增加。」George 一頓後續道，「而打藍絲，應該唔會。」<br />\n<br />\n抗爭的精力，轉移了去設路障、裝修、私了，都不是最令 George 無奈之處，最令他失望的，是發現前線愈來愈多，在他眼中只是「半桶水」的勇武抗爭者，「我哋會形容呢班人，叫偽勇武或者童子軍。」</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/再訪-屠龍小隊-勇武也到瓶頸了嗎\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E5%86%8D%E8%A8%AA-%E5%B1%A0%E9%BE%8D%E5%B0%8F%E9%9A%8A-%E5%8B%87%E6%AD%A6%E4%B9%9F%E5%88%B0%E7%93%B6%E9%A0%B8%E4%BA%86%E5%97%8E&d=30k2sE%2FAiGmcVOPaBnjddT2nqaxvu5zgGSEBmbQkQbg%3D&h=41b649d4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E5%86%8D%E8%A8%AA-%E5%B1%A0%E9%BE%8D%E5%B0%8F%E9%9A%8A-%E5%8B%87%E6%AD%A6%E4%B9%9F%E5%88%B0%E7%93%B6%E9%A0%B8%E4%BA%86%E5%97%8E&h=cfef7ddb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/再訪-屠龍小隊-勇武也到瓶頸了嗎</a>"},{"pid":"ad8a3651178ef25f2cfd79fa4c39c92b4c413fc2","tid":1706903,"uid":81236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T08:06:44.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"8aa860076787bc7975c9076753aab726cba5bcbb","tid":1706903,"uid":81236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T08:16:07.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"cac8a8d55987e8ec0e542d0c2846595c2a9abcfa","tid":1706903,"uid":81236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T09:21:22.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"3957e2d997563d7f8603d66ce888aa4d09a2d7b3","tid":1706903,"uid":192824,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T09:23:46.000Z","msg":"從來都唔駛問，反而嫌力度不夠<br />\n<br />\n緊記，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">肩，踭，膝，腕</span></span><br />\n<br />\n千奇唔好拉直隻腳，大大力成個人坐落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e884a69649d8381c0c8448da8a7bdbbcbd25346b","tid":1706903,"uid":2429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T09:24:04.000Z","msg":"做得好好。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fd59e8fab8d6f25b3079f476c929c906c3f91ed","tid":1706903,"uid":43737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T09:36:28.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n自己對於燒豬單野從來冇諗過要唔要割<br />\nfb都冇人提過,直至喺連登睇到第一個post先見到原來有人諗過割<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e804dd4642df3666f0a9bacfc4229a6ba929e96","tid":1706903,"uid":95588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T09:39:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fa68792b7acbd45499fe88ccae68169a37089fb","tid":1706903,"uid":81236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T11:22:39.000Z","msg":"唔好再問割唔割"},{"pid":"5162ea2a858b65593990970813f7231f80171299","tid":1706903,"uid":130695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T11:25:32.000Z","msg":"